Create container : sudo docker run -it --name my_interactive_container ubuntu:latest /bin/bash
List all containers : sudo docker ps -a
Start container : sudo docker start my_interactive_container
Attach to container : sudo docker attach my_interactive_container
Detach from container : Ctrl + p, Ctrl + q
Stop container : sudo docker stop my_interactive_container
Remove container : sudo docker rm my_interactive_container

Start Docker Service : 
    sudo systemctl start docker
    sudo systemctl enable docker
Stop Docker Service : 
    sudo systemctl stop docker
    sudo systemctl disable docker
Check Docker Status : 
    sudo systemctl status docker

How to Attach VS Code to a Running Container :
    Dev Containers: Attach to Running Container in command paletter